@leixuesong The `webpack` will only watch files which are built in the source (you can see `.temp` folder on your project).

So, If you want to watch it, you can modify the `webpack` config by yourself.

More detail you can see [Webpack Watch](https://webpack.js.org/configuration/watch/).

